---
title: Pulled Pork and Pineapple Tacos with Charred Corn Salsa and Lime Crema
description: If you think sweet and savoury combos are delicious, prepare to be blown away by these pulled pork and pineapple tacos, co-starring corn and kale! A zesty lime crema elevates this dish to a new family favourite!
